      About this item

      • Notes Before Buying: A Neutral wire is required, standard wall plate size. Treatlife 3-way dimmer switch works with 2.4GHz WiFi only( NOT 5G). Only for dimmable bulbs. The 3 way dimmer switch must be installed on the power source side, and the other end can only be connected to a standard/dumb 3-way. FCC certified. Flame-retardant material and built-in overheat protection for safety
      • 2 Master 3-Way Smart Dimmer Switches: For 2 different 3 way setups, only need 1 treatlife 3-way dimmer switch for each 3-way circuit. Comes with two main switches that can be used independently, you can install one to replace a current three-way setup in a hallway and use the other one in a bedroom. Can be used as a 3-way or single-pole switch. Just replace one traditional 3-way switch to control the light from 2 locations, best for the top and bottom of a staircase, garage and other large spaces
      • 1%-100% Dimming Range & Voice Control: This smart dimmer switch can adjust the brightness level from 1%-100% with Alexa and Google Assistant(not works with Homekit) voice assistants, it can easily control dimmable light by sending voice commands likeAlexa, dim the living room light to 30%." A brightness memory function is available for the wifi light switch to remember the last light setting when powered off
      • APP Remote Control & Schedule: This dimmer switch controls the light from anywhere and anytime by the Smart Life/Treatlife APP. You can set up schedules for the light to turn on/off according to your daily routines. Support setting countdown, sunrise and sunset timer. The smart light switch will automatically turn the light on with the preset brightness or off at specific times. It looks like someone is at home when you leave
      • Share Control & Reliable Support Services: Device sharing feature of the Alexa light switch allows you to share the control with your family. Let you and your family enjoy the proper atmosphere on different occasions by adjusting the brightness at any time. If you have any questions about your dimmer light switch, please contact us, and we will give you online installation assistance

      Product Description


      Networking Instructions:
      • No Hub Required
      • Secured 2.4GHz WiFi
      • Press and hold the on/off button for 5 seconds until the indicator light blinks rapidly
      • If the light remains red, the device is not connected
      • To reconnect after changing the router, hold the on/off button for 5 seconds to reconnect to the network

      Light up your life, your way - with our 3-way dimmer switch

      The 3-way dimmer smart switch lets you control all dimmer light bulbs with your phone. 0% - 100% smart dimming range can adjust the ambiance of the space better. From scheduling to creating scenes, the Smart Life app puts you in control, wherever you are.

      Using it as a 3-way smart switch to control the same light from 2 locations. Smart design for the top and bottom of stairs, perfect for large rooms with multiple entrances, etc.

      • Specifications:
      • Rated Voltage: 120V/60HZ
      • Max Power: 150W LED, 150W CFL, 400W INC
      • App Supported: Smart Life APP/ TreatLife APP
      • Wireless Standard: IEEE 802.11 b/g/n, 2.4GHz
      • Applicable Equipment: Non-smart but dimmable light bulbs
      • Best for top and bottom of a staircase, garage and other large spaces.

      Illuminate every moment perfectly with our advanced 3-way smart dimmer switch

      App/Manual Smart Dimming

      You can easily adjust the dimming level of 1% -100% by the button or APP, set the perfect ambiance light for any activities. Creating atmosphere on different occasions with desired brightness.

      Single-Pole and 3-way Application

      Using the 3-way smart dimmer switch as single pole or 3-way switch to control the light from 1 or 2 locations. Just replace one traditional 3-way switch to control the light from 2 locations. It will save more money and power.

      Group Control

      Add a group of Treatlife smart dimmer switch to control a collection of lights. When your family and friends arrive at the agreed location, you can turn on all lights in the house with one click. It makes the party full of surprises and fun!

      Create the perfect ambiance at home with ease. Upgrade to our 3-way smart dimmer switch and enjoy customizable lighting for every occasion

      Device Share

      Just tap the button in the smart life APP, you can share your dimmer smart plug to all family members. It makes your family relationships closer and makes your life easier and smarter.

      Gentle Off

      The smart switch allows fade off the lights in the child's bedroom after turning on the switch, so that the baby's eyes will never be shocked by too bright light.

      Easy Setup

      No need to understand complex 3-way wiring, step-by-step instructions will guide you through the wiring process. Excellent customer support is always behind you to help at any time.

      Q1: My switch isn't working in my home circuit.

      Please ensure that your home circuit has a neutral wire, as our switch requires it for compatibility. Circuits without a neutral wire are not suitable for our switch. It's essential to install only one 3-way dimmer switch per circuit. Place the switch on the side near the power source for optimal operation.

      Q2: The light connected to the switch is flashing unexpectedly.

      To address flashing light issues, use one of the three compatibility modes available on the app. Refer to the user manual for specific steps. Note: Our product is not compatible with lights that come with a remote control; using it may cause flashing when adjusting brightness. Additionally, an unstable network may result in flickering lights.

      Q3: The switch isn't functioning properly despite the correct wiring.

      During the wiring process, tighten the wire cap securely, failure to do so may prevent the switch from receiving power, leading to malfunctions. Please recognize the importance of proper wiring for normal operation. Consult the troubleshooting steps in the user manual for proper installation.

      Q4: I can't pair the switch with the app.

      Ensure pairing occurs in the 2.4 GHz network frequency band, as our switch doesn't support pairing in the 5 GHz frequency band. The switch must connect to the network within the specified 3-minute pairing time to avoid connection failure. Follow the pairing steps outlined in the user manual for successful integration.

      Q5: Master 3-Way Smart Dimmer Switch Usage.

      The 3-way dimmable switch can be used as a 3-way or single-pole main switch, you can install it to replace a current 3-way setup in a hallway or your bedroom. Just replace one of the two 3-way dimmer switches and leave your other existing 3-way switch in place. Make sure to install Treatlife switch on the line side (the source of power) and the 3-way switch on the other end needs to be a standard/dumb 3-way.

        4.0 out of 5 stars Great products, easy to install and the app is good! However, it has one design flaw.
        Reviewed in the United States on July 30, 2022
        Style: 2PackVerified Purchase
        So I have converted all my home switches and dimmers with treatlife products and overall I highly recommend them. Here the key things to consider, the good and the bad.

        DESIGN: The design is great and they come with face plates as well. The face plates are snap-on style which is great as it dosent show those screws that traditional plates show. However, if you still want your traditional plates, you can use them as the switches have the provision to put screws on.

        INSTALLATION: The installation is very easy and the instructions are very easy to follow. Make sure you have a NEUTRAL WIRE, typically the white wire. The box comes complete with wire nuts, screws etc. But the best part is that it comes with little pre-printed lables that you can put on your existing wires which makes installation Very easy. I did have to buy some larger wire nuts for my ground and neutral as some of them already were 4 cables and adding another 1 was too big for the wire nuts provided.

        INTEGRATION: was very easily able to integrate them with the treatlife app, and then with Google Home and SmartThings app. You can build your scenes/or IFTTT within treatlife app itself and the app has timer functions built in. Google Home commands are very intuitive. I was able to build a scene in google home to turn the downstairs or upstairs or the entire hime light as a group quickly. Further, I was easily able to build IFTTT for some secondary rooms (like pantry or garage) to auto-turn off after set amount of time everytime automatically.

        THE BAD STUFF:
        My only problem with the three pole dimmer is that it leaves the second dimmer on the circuit useless. So, as per treatlife customer service, you only need to replace one dimmer on a two dimmer circuit on the lead side. I had traditional dimmers on the circuit on both ends and I was able to control my lights with either dimmer. Now, after installing the treatlife 3 pole dimmer, the smart dimmer works great, but the second dimmer is useless. So if I want to not use it as a smart dimmer, I have to walk to the treatlife dimmer and use it. But it does work fine with google voice command etc. I checked with treatlife customer service and they confirmed the 2nd switch cant be a dimmer, it should be a non-smart switch. I think this is a desing flaw and should be fixed somehow.

        Hope this review helps.

        Enjoy!
